
   ===== Module trigger bus (rows) <-> Backplane (cols) trigger matrix =====

                                   === Backplane Lines (2 bit/col!) ===
                                 /- B6: Busy (typ. OUT)
                                 |  /- B5: General Purpose (IN/OUT)
                                 |  |  /- B4: Readout Request (typ. OUT)
                                 |  |  |  /- B3: General Purpose (IN/OUT)
                                 |  |  |  |  /- B2: Readout Trigger T3 (typ. IN)
                                 |  |  |  |  |  /- B1: Readout Trigger T2 (unused), G.P. (IN/OUT)
                                 |  |  |  |  |  |  /- B0: Readout Trigger T1 (typ. IN)
 == module triger lines ==      6| 5| 4| 3| 2| 1| 0| 
 *.*.iomatrix_gpt1               .  I  .  .  .  .  .   0b00010000000000 aka 0x0400 
 *.*.iomatrix_gpt2               .  .  .  O  .  .  .   0b00000010000000 aka 0x0080 
 *.*.iomatrix_gpt3               .  .  .  .  .  .  .   0b00000000000000 aka 0x0000 
 *.*.iomatrix_gpt4               .  .  .  .  .  .  .   0b00000000000000 aka 0x0000 
 *.*.iomatrix_t1                 .  .  .  .  .  .  I   0b00000000000001 aka 0x0001 
 *.*.iomatrix_t3                 .  .  .  .  I  .  .   0b00000000010000 aka 0x0010 
 *.*.iomatrix_rorq               .  .  O  .  .  .  .   0b00001000000000 aka 0x0200 
