                                 /- 9: (0x200) proton discriminator
                                 |  /- 8: (0x100) gamma discriminator
                                 |  |  /- 7: (0x80) timing discriminator 
                                 |  |  |   ==== module trigger bus ====
                                 |  |  |  /- 6: (0x40) Readout Request   
                                 |  |  |  |  /- 5: (0x20) Readout T3 (src only)
                                 |  |  |  |  |  /- 4: (0x10) Readout T1 (src only)
                                 |  |  |  |  |  |  /- 3: (0x8) GPT4
                                 |  |  |  |  |  |  |  /- 2: (0x4) GPT3
                                 |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  /- 1: (0x2) GPT2 
                                 |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  /- 0: (0x1) GPT1
